assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlplQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0d740b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723e5fe722ac905665aef6670ee91e4f379358cd","tid":1795724,"uid":183912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"自推六下"},{"pid":"7da53033968a16fa2c5cecff17e9c5994e439346","tid":1795724,"uid":183912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8f691bfa9807a50ab528f8ebc310e956219c720d","tid":1795724,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"留証據, 再去勞工處告條仆街."},{"pid":"7f5bc470b06f262c74a1bc16694ca8df3dcf8b52","tid":1795724,"uid":183912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f691bfa9807a50ab528f8ebc310e956219c720d","tid":1795724,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"留証據, 再去勞工處告條仆街."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:13:34.000Z","msg":"無用"},{"pid":"12137426e99b606022ee58a2a69e108a3ae7dd8c","tid":1795724,"uid":183912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,